  "label": "induction over N (via Set(N))",
  "status": "axiom",
  "gloss": "for all S : Set(N), if 0 is in S and S is closed under successor, then every n : N is in S. Second-order induction in two-sorted first-order clothing; Dedekind-categorical under full semantics, Henkin caveat recorded in design SS2.2.",
